        <trans-unit id="103" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>You can do form-based data-access programming with class <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>CFormView<ept id="p1">](../mfc/reference/cformview-class.md)</ept>, but <bpt id="p2">[</bpt>CRecordView<ept id="p2">](../mfc/reference/crecordview-class.md)</ept> and <bpt id="p3">[</bpt>CDaoRecordView<ept id="p3">](../mfc/reference/cdaorecordview-class.md)</ept> are generally better classes to derive from.</source>
        </trans-unit>
